Description: ==========
        urlpathlib
        ==========
        
        This module offers classes representing paths with semantics appropriate for
        local and remote resources.
        
        Install
        =======
        
        Simply run the following command::
        
          pip install urlpathlib
        
        
        Features
        ========
        
        Supported protocols:
        
        +---------------------------------------+--------------------+----------+
        | protocol                              | scheme             | support  |
        +=======================================+====================+==========+
        | local filesystem                      | file://            | **✓**    |
        +---------------------------------------+--------------------+----------+
        | HTTP                                  | http://            | **✓**    |
        +---------------------------------------+--------------------+----------+
        
        Supported IO operations:
        
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | method name              | file://    | http[s]:// |
        +==========================+============+============+
        | chmod                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | exists                   | **✓**      | **✓**      |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | expanduser               | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | glob                     | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | group                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_block_device          | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_char_device           | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_dir                   | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_fifo                  | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_file                  | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_socket                | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | is_symlink               | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | iterdir                  | **✓**      | **✓**¹     |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | lchmod                   | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | lstat                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | mkdir                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | open                     | **✓**      | **✓**      |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | read_bytes               | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | read_text                | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | rename                   | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | replace                  | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | resolve                  | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | rglob                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | rmdir                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | samefile                 | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | stat                     | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | symlink_to               | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | touch                    | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | unlink                   | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | write_bytes              | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        | write_text               | **✓**      |            |
        +--------------------------+------------+------------+
        
        Notes:
        
        ¹: only binary read is supported at the moment.
        
Platform: any
